# NOTE: do NOT add data/processed/*.csv or *.json here. The dashboard's
# cold-start bootstrap (dashboard/app.py: ensure_pipeline_artifacts) only
# does a cheap SQLite rebuild when these already exist; if they were ever
# gitignored, every fresh deploy (e.g. Streamlit Community Cloud) would
# silently pay for a full survival-model refit on every cold start instead.
